1999_August 31 

Why oh why is this film so good? Is it because the cast click together so
well you'd think they were a real life family? Is it because the plot
scores
so high on originality? Or maybe it's just because it's an amazing piece
of
science fiction that will delight any movie fan from the USA to the Fiji
Islands! Well , whatever the reason may be , i can tell you it gets my
vote
as one of the best movies ever made!
